{"word":"συμβουλευτέος","slug":"συμβουλευτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμβουλευτέος</b></el> <el>(συμβουλευτέος, η, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:συμβουλεύω'><el>συμβουλεύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be given as advice</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>-τέον</el>, <i>one must advise</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}